{"tid":1076120,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【歐國盃外圍賽】波蘭賽前爆流感　8將中招　元凶疑為前鋒A Milik","createTime":"2019-03-24T15:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T01:41:32.000Z","uid":199518,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb78b4ca223ecb318baaa845e451bc77e05af57","tid":1076120,"uid":199518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:14:31.000Z","msg":"歐國盃外圍賽進行得如火如荼之際，G組波蘭隊卻爆發流感鬧兵荒。前鋒比亞迪克及米利克等最少8人中招，明晨迎戰拉脫維亞需抱病上陣。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭歐國外G組首仗作客險勝奧地利1：0，但中場施連斯基比賽撞傷背部，明晨上陣成疑。主帥比斯錫（Jerzy Brzeczek）賽前卻帶來更壞消息：「隊內爆發流感，一共有8名球員染病，包括比亞迪克。」他續指守將碧拿歷克和比列薩尼斯基昨日也沒操練，並歸咎於作客維也納時酒店的冷氣問題。<br />\n<br />\n不過比斯錫也提到最先有病徵的是米利克，而這名拿玻里前鋒有可能是帶菌者，因為其球會隊友法比安彭拿早前發燒送院，確診豬流感，因而退出西班牙隊。拿玻里門將阿歷斯美列特同樣因病未能為意大利U21上陣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/article/20190324/s00006/1553427383943/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%90%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%83%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8D%E8%B3%BD%E3%80%91%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E8%B3%BD%E5%89%8D%E7%88%86%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F-8%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B-%E5%85%83%E5%87%B6%E7%96%91%E7%82%BA%E5%89%8D%E9%8B%92%E7%B1%B3%E5%88%A9%E5%85%8B?fbclid=IwAR0cDiXlfngf4tgqhM_USXBFsDffExlSSkiSepYntbTG2mEGIdBWLc5VrkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2Farticle%2F20190324%2Fs00006%2F1553427383943%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%2590%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%259B%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%258D%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%2598%25AD%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%2584%259F-8%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258B%259B-%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2587%25B6%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%258B%2592%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2585%258B%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0cDiXlfngf4tgqhM_USXBFsDffExlSSkiSepYntbTG2mEGIdBWLc5VrkU&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6Qp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=f63a67a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2Farticle%2F20190324%2Fs00006%2F15